problems.L:
sumLeft[i] — sum of first i weights, sumRight[i] — sum of last i weights.

Solution in pseudocode:

```
  ans = inf;
  for i = 0 .. n {
    curr = firstSum[i] * l + lastSum[n-i] * r;
    if ( i > n - i ) curr = curr + (2i - n - 1) * Ql;
    if ( i < n - i ) curr = curr + (n - 2i - 1) * Qr;

    ans = min(ans, curr);
  }

```

Time complexity: O(n).
